These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, dunhill, siglo
1. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
3. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Cigar   | bongani | blend | dunhill | siglo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, may, april
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Birthday   | june | march | april | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, soul, disco, rock
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco | soul | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, handball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Sport   | weightlifting | swimming | tennis | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
