.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, train, subway
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the subway##2
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Transport   | subway | boat | airplane | train |

